Key Match Events: Jason Heyward hit a go-ahead, two-run homer
Alex Bregman homered in the first inning
Randy Arozarena doubled and scored a run in the third inning
Jose Altuve, Yordan Alvarez, and Michael Brantley did not record a hit
Post-Match Reflections: Framber Valdez improved to 16-7 with the win
Logan Gilbert fell to 9-13 with the loss
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Astros clinched their fourth consecutive AL West title
Others: The game lasted 2 hours and 26 minutes
Umpires for the game were Marvin Hudson, Hunter Wendelstedt, Nick Mahrley, and John Tumpane
